    "Belt, she became an art history lecturer at Pomona College.</p>\n<p>Her time in Hannover was quite possibly the most consequential period of her life, where she not only raised a family, but also advanced the emerging avant-garde arts scene, created her own publishing company, and wrote a series of children\u2019s books alongside her business partner Kurt Schwitters.": [],
